Alec J. Schramm \Lambda

and Daniel H. Reeves Department of Physics, Occidental College, Los Angeles, CA 90041

Abstract We estimate the impact parameter dependence of the production cross section for jc and jb mesons in peripheral heavy-ion collisions collisions. Total and elastic flfl cross sections are calculated in an equivalent photon approximation. 13.75.Cs,25.75.+r

